field_description: 5-character FIPS code
1-character ownership code
6-character Industry Code (NAICS, SuperSector)
2-character aggregation level code
1-character size code
4-character year
1-character quarter (always A for annual)
1-character disclosure code (either ' '(blank) or 'N' not disclosed)
Multi-character area title associated with the area's FIPS (Excluded from singlefile)
Multi-character ownership title associated with the ownership code (Excluded from singlefile)
Multi-character industry title associated with the industry code (Excluded from singlefile)
Multi-character aggregation title associated with the agglvl code (Excluded from singlefile)
Multi-character size title associated with the size code (Excluded from singlefile)
Count of establishments for a given quarter
Employment level for the first month of a given quarter
Employment level for the second month of a given quarter
Employment level for the third month of a  given quarter
Total wages for a given quarter
Taxable wages for a given quarter
Quarterly contributions for a given quarter
Average weekly wage for a given quarter
1-character location-quotient disclosure code (either ' '(blank) or 'N' not disclosed
Location quotient of the quarterly establishment count relative to the U.S. (Rounded to hundredths place)
Location quotient of the emloyment level for the first month of a given quarter relative to the U.S. (Rounded to hundredths place)
Location quotient of the emloyment level for the second month of a given quarter relative to the U.S. (Rounded to hundredths place)
Location quotient of the emloyment level for the third month of a given quarter relative to the U.S. (Rounded to hundredths place)
Location quotient of the total wages for a given quarter relative to the U.S. (Rounded to hundredths place)
Location quotient of the total taxable wages for a given quarter relative to the U.S. (Rounded to hundredths place)
Location quotient of the total contributions for a given quarter relative to the U.S. (Rounded to hundredths place)
Location quotient of the average weekly wage for a given quarter relative to the U.S. (Rounded to hundredths place)
1-character over-the-year disclosure code (either ' '(blank) or 'N' not disclosed)
Over-the-year change in the count of establishments for a given quarter
Over-the-year percent change in the count of establishments for a given quarter (Rounded to the tenths place)
Over-the-year change in the first month's employment level of a given quarter
Over-the-year percent change in the first month's employment level of a given quarter (Rounded to the tenths place)
Over-the-year change in the second month's employment level of a given quarter
Over-the-year percent change in the second month's employment level of a given quarter (Rounded to the tenths place)
Over-the-year change in the third month's employment level of a given quarter
Over-the-year percent change in the third month's employment level of a given quarter (Rounded to the tenths place)
Over-the-year change in total quarterly wages for a given quarter
Over-the-year percent change in total quarterly wages for a given quarter (Rounded to the tenths place)
Over-the-year change in taxable quarterly wages for a given quarter
Over-the-year percent change in taxable quarterly wages for a given quarter (Rounded to the tenths place)
Over-the-year change in quarterly contributions for a given quarter
Over-the-year percent change in quarterly contributions for a given quarter (Rounded to the tenths place)
Over-the-year change in average weekly wage for a given quarter
Over-the-year percent change in average weekly wage for a given quarter (Rounded to the tenths place)
